<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>MUSTBEE 账号绑定</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row header">
      <h1>MUSTBEE</h1>
      
    </div>
    <div class="row description">
      <span>请填写正确的学生卡号与密码以完成绑定</span>
    </div>
    <form class='loginForm' action="http://ec2-54-84-201-78.compute-1.amazonaws.com/login" method="post" >
      <div class="form-group col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <label for="stuID">学生卡号</label>
        <input class='form-control' type="text" name="studentID" id="stuID" placeholder="如：1409853A-B123-5678">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <label for="stuPWD">密码</label>
        <input class='form-control' type="password" name="pwd" id="studentPWD">
      </div>
      <div class='col-md-4 col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-offset-4 col-xs-offset-4 col-sm-offset-4'>
        <input type="submit" value="绑定" class='btn btn-default '>
      </div>
      
  </form>
  </div>
  
  
</body>
</html>